      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 1.2",
      "text": "φοβεῖται τὸν",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 1.3",
      "text": "πατέρα κᾀσχύνεται, οὗτος",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 1.4",
      "text": "πολίτης ἀγαθὸς ἔσται κατὰ λόγον, καὶ τοὺς",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 1.5",
      "text": "πολεμίους δυνάμενος κακῶς",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 1.6",
      "text": "ποιεῖν.",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 2.1",
      "text": "Τἀργύριόν ἐστιν αἷμα καὶ ψυχὴ βροτοῖς. ὅστις δὲ μὴ ἔχει",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 2.2",
      "text": "τοῦτο μηδ’ ἐκτήσατο, οὗτος μετὰ ζώντων",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 2.3",
      "text": "τεθνηκὼς",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 2.4",
      "text": "περιπατεῖ.",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 3.1",
      "text": "Χῖοι",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 3.2",
      "text": "πολὺ ἄριστ’ ἀνευρήκασιν ὀψαρτυτικήν.",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
